data.description: An inviting 2-bedroom home with an additional 2 rooms in the basement with a spacious yard perfect for hosting this summer. This charming home features beautiful hardwood floors. Enjoy the peace of mind with a brand new roof and gutters, while the newer tuck pointing adds to the home's overall durability. The washing machine is about 2 yrs old and the water heater is about 5yrs old. The furnace and A/C, both approximately 10 years old, contribute to the home's enduring comfort. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this well-maintained property your future home!  AS-IS property
